{"tid":322308,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[求救]MBP登入後發光黑mon","createTime":"2017-07-14T16:59:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-14T17:49:58.000Z","uid":36673,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5876a620ca260ce98b57e8453064cdaac07af6d4","tid":322308,"uid":36673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T16:59:33.000Z","msg":"MBP，開到機去到登入畫面，登入後發光黑mon，見到cursor，brightness 個埋全部較到有反應，但就係load唔到desktop畫面個堆野出黎<br />\n<br />\n試左安全模式、清 PRAM、SMC都唔得<br />\n前兩日仲正常用到，更新左去OS Sierra之後都仲用到，係今日一開機就出事<br />\n<br />\n請各位巴打打救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e6a5c17362904c97b65224621889efc47d7f1e9","tid":322308,"uid":36673,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T17:49:58.000Z","msg":"已解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幫助其他苦主：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">roseauxyw 02-05 15:53 8#<br />\n我也碰到这个问题了 command+r重新安装更新/重置SMC/重置PRAM 也不能解决<br />\ngoogle了下解决办法 发现是安全更新到一半被打断导致没有安装好的问题（我没关机合盖休眠 可能后台正在更新吧）<br />\n解决办法：<br />\n1.强制关机后 按住shift进入安全模式开机<br />\n2.黑屏后 只有鼠标指针，这时键入电脑账户用户名的首字母一次  然后按tab 再输入登陆密码 最后回车 （这个过程是黑屏的）<br />\n3.过一会鼠标变成彩虹轮了，再过一会出现了更新系统的界面 等到读条结束就能进入系统了<br />\n4.然后重启一次<br />\n就好了<br />\n希望对你有帮助 我也苦恼了好久了，手边又没有大的移动硬盘可以备份的，不想格盘重来。</span>"}]}